    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive controls</h2>Jump into the real-sized driver’s seat, turn up the volume, and feel the speed and the kick of adrenaline. Enjoy the VR-native controls: turn the wheel with your hands, adjust mirrors, and control the gearbox and car computer. Your car is so much more in virtual reality!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/18ebe107fd472cac444028ca9a228477.poster.avif?t=1726560687\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/18ebe107fd472cac444028ca9a228477.webm?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/18ebe107fd472cac444028ca9a228477.mp4?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real licensed cars</h2>Have you ever imagined what it would be like to get in the seat of the <i>Nissan GT-R 2021 Track Edition</i>? Or maybe <i>Jaguar XE SV Project 8</i>? Say no more because you will have a real car and real feelings here.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/a5419756862c7220fb7b02f0d02c8947.poster.avif?t=1726560687\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/a5419756862c7220fb7b02f0d02c8947.webm?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/a5419756862c7220fb7b02f0d02c8947.mp4?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compete and hang out with real people</h2>Have fun with your friends or find new ones. Race or chill in the lobby, play mini-games, show off your car and your style, challenge racers, listen to music and celebrate car culture with the others.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/872976fd406c843d6823d1d20caf7f8e.poster.avif?t=1726560687\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/872976fd406c843d6823d1d20caf7f8e.webm?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/872976fd406c843d6823d1d20caf7f8e.mp4?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>Customize your car in different visual and technical variations, and develop your builds to achieve a unique gaming style and appearance.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/7076ab5d3c6d7ca8f395d19515b00a99.poster.avif?t=1726560687\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/7076ab5d3c6d7ca8f395d19515b00a99.webm?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/7076ab5d3c6d7ca8f395d19515b00a99.mp4?t=1726560687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
